Package: fieldwalkr
Type: Package
Title: Spatial Sampling and Survey Simulation Tools
Version: 0.2
Date: 2016-02-21
Authors@R: person("Joe", "Roe", email = "jwg983@hum.ku.dk",
  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: fieldwalkr is a simulation framework for exploring, designing, and
  evaluating sampling strategies in for spatial surveys (fieldwalking in
  archaeology jargon).
Depends: R (>= 3.2.2)
License: MIT + file LICENSE
LazyData: TRUE
